## 2. Code Quality & Component Architecture

### 🛡️ ProcessGuard Validation 
- **Status:** Active & Compliant.
- **Analysis:** [scripts/process_guard.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/process_guard.py) is successfully integrated into the central training pipeline. It has transcended the reactive posture of legacy `judge_guard` and now performs real-time continuous validation. It actively monitors iteration metrics and uses JSON-structured exception handling to gracefully degrade instead of crashing, preserving the agent's autonomy and dialetical learning loop.

### 🛠️ ToolRegistry & Elite Techniques
- **Status:** Modularized & Domain-Independent.
- **Analysis:** The [scripts/tool_registry.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/tool_registry.py) completely decouples advanced operations from fixed domains. Elite techniques, specifically [tabular_rag](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/tool_registry.py#35-44) and [cross_domain_features](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/tool_registry.py#45-50), are now deployed as plug-and-play decorators. Hardcoded column dependencies have been entirely phased out, allowing true multi-competition reuse.

### 💾 MemoryIntegrity Optimization (Rule 27)
- **Status:** Optimized & High-Performance.
- **Analysis:** [scripts/memory_integrity.py](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/memory_integrity.py) has been fully refactored to comply with Rule 27. It correctly splits metadata from raw storage. Microactions are rapidly written to optimized binary `.parquet` files via PyArrow, effectively eliminating memory congestion. Cryptographic SHA-256 integrity hashing is strictly reserved for primary dialectical milestones (`thesis`, `antithesis`, `synthesis`).

## 3. Deviation from 3-6-2 Dialectic Protocol
- **Historical Deviation:** Previously, fixed thresholds inside the main text prompt constrained the agent, creating "cognitive dissonance" and disrupting the 3-6-2 dialectical cycle during edge-case dataset tasks. Furthermore, the memory module's aggressive hashing caused severe iteration bottlenecking.
- **Current Alignment:** These deviations have been resolved. The movement of fixed parameter thresholds into the domain-specific [trinity_config.json](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/trinity_config.json) allows the agent to dynamically adapt without modifying the core Constitution. The system is structurally primed to run rapid Thesis-Antithesis-Synthesis cycles indefinitely.

